♪The world's many twists
end in separation♪

701
00:31:31,155 --> 00:31:34,835
♪I can't bear to watch♪

702
00:31:35,535 --> 00:31:39,985
♪This mortal world is full of hardships♪

703
00:31:39,985 --> 00:31:44,325
♪Alas, this fate is full of misfortune♪

704
00:31:44,825 --> 00:31:47,445
♪But I refuse to accept♪

705
00:31:47,445 --> 00:31:52,305
♪That regret is
the only natural outcome♪

706
00:31:52,675 --> 00:31:57,455
♪So, I cross mountains and rivers♪

707
